Because when you look at a project, you say, well, let me see what the release is on GitHub.

00:23:48.460 --> 00:23:53.980
If you know that literally that was the thing that compiled or got built and then that's

00:23:54.080 --> 00:23:56.320
what's on PyPI, that's a different...

00:23:58.240 --> 00:23:59.640
forensic analysis than

00:24:01.660 --> 00:24:02.340
somebody's machine.

