00:25:06.340 --> 00:25:10.680
is now an official numbering authority. So rather than saying there's a problem with Python,

00:25:11.740 --> 00:25:16.380
who is going to sort of officially call this out and write it up and so on,

00:25:16.440 --> 00:25:18.280
Like you guys can do that directly now, right?

