00:26:56.280 --> 00:27:02.040
make sure that it's not confusing. So by owning the entire process, we're able to make sure that

00:27:02.200 --> 00:27:07.040
things are as little confusing as possible. Like what actually needs to be done for users.

00:27:07.180 --> 00:27:08.760
when we publish these things.

