01:02:22.600 --> 01:02:23.420
It is lovely.

01:02:24.200 --> 01:02:25.880
One of the things that's most important to me

01:02:25.880 --> 01:02:28.040
is this whole aspect of storytelling.

01:02:28.700 --> 01:02:30.940
And so that's why I felt really, really happy

01:02:30.960 --> 01:02:31.760
that I was invited along

01:02:32.060 --> 01:02:33.700
to be able to tell these stories to all of you.

01:02:33.960 --> 01:02:37.060
And I think that having all of these different narratives

01:02:38.140 --> 01:02:40.340
all in one place of all of these huge themes

01:02:40.800 --> 01:02:43.720
about what Python is going through all at once, right?

01:02:43.940 --> 01:02:45.500
Like it's really incredible

01:02:46.420 --> 01:02:49.040
how many different things are happening

01:02:49.420 --> 01:02:50.400
in Python all at once.

01:02:50.600 --> 01:02:52.560
And like sometimes when you're focusing

01:02:52.580 --> 01:02:58.720
just one or just two, you don't have this huge context of, wow, Python is changing in at least

01:02:59.080 --> 01:03:04.220
20 different ways all at once. And we're somehow doing really, really well, I would say. I have no

01:03:04.660 --> 01:03:12.300
doubt about any of these huge changes that Python is going through to take it in the wrong direction.

01:03:12.420 --> 01:03:15.740
I'm feeling hopeful and excited about all of them. So it's an exciting time.

01:03:16.240 --> 01:03:22.400
Yeah, I am as well. And it is really tricky to get a holistic picture of the progress.

01:03:22.480 --> 01:03:26.940
because there's a lot of different groups doing different things

01:03:27.050 --> 01:03:31.240
and there's no one person's or one company's job

01:03:31.460 --> 01:03:33.620
to get somebody to come and tell that story.

01:03:33.840 --> 01:03:36.380
So, yeah, thanks for giving us the insight here.

01:03:36.440 --> 01:03:36.800
It's been awesome.

01:03:38.460 --> 01:03:41.100
Thanks for being on the show, and I'm sure we'll have you back soon.

01:03:41.840 --> 01:03:43.420
Yeah, sounds good. Thanks for having me.

01:03:43.700 --> 01:03:44.120
See you.

01:03:44.900 --> 01:03:44.980
Bye.

